This article describes brie5y the purposes of the workshop, the material covered, and the resulting recommendations and conclusions: no attempt has been made to cover all aspects of the workshop. A full workshop report is being prepared and will appear in early 1990. Electronic mail may be sent to { m89@ora.on.ca} for information pertaining to the availability of the report. The report also includes descriptions of forty-three projects that have significant formal methods components. This article is based on a draft of the workshop report PI.